snippet.title: Ultimate Golf - ultimate courses, ultimate competition!
snippet.description:
We're celebrating Ultimate Golf turning One Year Old with this slick new ad! 

Stunning Real Life courses. The most Badass Golf Balls in gaming. This is the Ultimate No-wait PvP golf game that you'll love to beat your buds at. 

Think you've got the makings of a real player? Give it a watch, get in the game, tell us what you think! 

Come say hi on Facebook: 
https://www.facebook.com/ultimategolfgame
